---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Promocionar mi Inmueble - Portada Inmobiliaria">
    <div class="min-h-screen pt-28 w-full flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="relative w-full h-screen flex flex-col">
            <img class="w-full h-screen object-cover object-center brightness-[30%]" src="/img/personal.webp" alt="">
            <div class="absolute h-full flex justify-center">
                <div class="flex space-x-10 justify-center items-center mx-5">
                <!-- Primera Columna -->
                <div class="w-1/2 flex justify-center">
                    <p class="text-white uppercase font-extrabold text-5xl text-center text-balance tracking-wide">¿Qué esperas para arrendar tu inmueble con nosotros?</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Segunda Columna -->
                <div class="w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center items-center h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-900 shadow-custom">
                    <p class="text-white text-center text-balance text-2xl px-4">Nuestro equipo de asesores comerciales altamente capacitados se encargará de promocionar tu propiedad y gestionar eficientemente los trámites de arrendamiento. Confía en nuestra experiencia y arrienda tu inmueble con nosotros.</p>
                    <button class="text-xl uppercase text-black font-bold mt-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-200 p-4 rounded-full hover:from-white hover:to-gray-300 shadow-custom">Dejanos tus datos</button>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- CARDS PROPUESTAS DE VALOR -->
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center mt-28 mb-28">
        <div class="line w-20 bg-red-600 h-1"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <span class="text-4xl font-bold ml-5 mr-5">Nuestra Propuesta de Valor</span>
            </div>
        <div class="line w-20 bg-red-600 h-1"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="flex items-center relative w-full justify-center">
            <div class="absolute right-[3%] card h-[350px] p-8 flex w-60 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-800 to-red-950 border-2 border-gray-200 text-white flex-col justify-center items-center space-y-3">
                <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-flag" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M5 5a5 5 0 0 1 7 0a5 5 0 0 0 7 0v9a5 5 0 0 1 -7 0a5 5 0 0 0 -7 0v-9z" /><path d="M5 21v-7" /></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="uppercase font-bold text-2xl text-balance text-center">Avisos Publicitarios</span>
                <span class="text-center">Instalamos vallas y avisos en todos nuestros inmuebles</span>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute right-[20%] card h-[400px] p-8 flex w-72 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-700 to-red-900 border-2 border-gray-200 justify-center flex-col text-white items-center space-y-3">
                <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-browser-check" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M4 4m0 1a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h14a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v14a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-14a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1z" /><path d="M4 8h16" /><path d="M8 4v4" /><path d="M9.5 14.5l1.5 1.5l3 -3" /></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="uppercase font-bold text-2xl text-balance text-center">Redes Sociales</span>
                <span class="text-center">Potenciamos la visibilidad de tu inmueble en las plataformas sociales más relevantes.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="card h-[420px] p-8 flex w-72 rounded-2xl z-[5] bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 border-2 flex-col justify-center text-white items-center space-y-3">
                <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-trending-up" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M3 17l6 -6l4 4l8 -8" /><path d="M14 7l7 0l0 7" /></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="uppercase font-bold text-3xl text-balance text-center">Asi promocionamos tu inmueble</span>
                <span class="text-center">Destacamos tu propiedad con estrategias de marketing personalizadas.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-[20%] card h-[400px] p-8 flex w-72 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-900 to-red-700 border-2 border-gray-200 z-[2] flex-col justify-center items-center text-white space-y-3">
                <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-home-dollar" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M19 10l-7 -7l-9 9h2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h6" /><path d="M9 21v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h2c.387 0 .748 .11 1.054 .3" /><path d="M21 15h-2.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3h1a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0 3h-2.5" /><path d="M19 21v1m0 -8v1" /></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="uppercase font-bold text-2xl text-balance text-center">Portales Inmobiliarios</span>
                <span class="text-center mt-2">Finca Raíz, Metro Cuadrado, CienCuadras, Afydi, Idonde</span>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-[3%] card h-[350px] p-8 flex w-60 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-950 to-red-800 border-2 border-gray-200 z-0 flex-col justify-center items-center text-white space-y-3">
                <span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-world-www" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M19.5 7a9 9 0 0 0 -7.5 -4a8.991 8.991 0 0 0 -7.484 4" /><path d="M11.5 3a16.989 16.989 0 0 0 -1.826 4" /><path d="M12.5 3a16.989 16.989 0 0 1 1.828 4" /><path d="M19.5 17a9 9 0 0 1 -7.5 4a8.991 8.991 0 0 1 -7.484 -4" /><path d="M11.5 21a16.989 16.989 0 0 1 -1.826 -4" /><path d="M12.5 21a16.989 16.989 0 0 0 1.828 -4" /><path d="M2 10l1 4l1.5 -4l1.5 4l1 -4" /><path d="M17 10l1 4l1.5 -4l1.5 4l1 -4" /><path d="M9.5 10l1 4l1.5 -4l1.5 4l1 -4" /></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="uppercase font-bold text-2xl text-balance text-center">Nuestra Pagina Web</span>
                <span class="text-center">Potenciamos la visibilidad de tu propiedad en nuestra página web.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>